    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium-high heat with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chicken breast </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until browned on both sides</p><p>Add your<strong> Tenderstem broccoli</strong> to the baking tray with the <strong>vegetables</strong> for the last 10-12 min of cooking time</p>",
