    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil a kettle</p><p>Meanwhile, divide the <strong>sage & onion stuffing</strong> into 2 per person and shape into <strong>stuffing balls</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>stuffing balls</strong> to a baking tray and put them in the oven for 10-12 min or until they're browned</p>",
